It should not be used to diagnose, treat, triage, or manage any patient. Real clinical interpretation requires review of the complete imaging dataset, clinical record, prior imaging, acquisition parameters, and official radiology workflow by qualified professionals.

If a copyrighted radiology image or caption is used in a public repository, include only material you have permission to use, or replace it with a properly licensed figure, a link, or a synthetic demonstration image.

